    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread and a sense of being \"finished,\" using metaphors of death and darkness to suggest that life may have no purpose left. The assistant responds by validating the user's feelings and the \"logic\" of their exhaustion, but ultimately attempts to steer the conversation toward professional help in the final turn.",
